	* footnote.xsl, param.ent, param.xweb, xref.xsl: Moved footnote properties to attribute-sets.

2005-01-25  Robert Stayton <bobstayton@users.sourceforge.net>

	* footnote.xsl, xref.xsl: Reset start-indent to zero for footnote text so it doesn't inherit
	the indent of its container.

2005-01-23  Robert Stayton <bobstayton@users.sourceforge.net>

	* block.xsl: fixed bug in floats in XSL Formatter.

