	* block.xsl: Added support for side floats, margin notes, and custom floats.

	* pagesetup.xsl: Add new parameters body.start.indent and body.end.indent to
	the set.flow.properties template.

	* param.ent, param.xweb: Added new parameters to support side floats and margin notes.

