	* index.xsl: Moved hardcoded properties for index division titles to
	the index.div.title.properties attribute-set.

	* lists.xsl: xep supports table-layout="auto" now.

	* param.ent, param.xweb: Added index.entry.properties attribute-set.

	* param.ent, param.xweb: Added index.div.title.properties attribute-set.

	* xref.xsl: Pass $verbose parameter to most elements.

